 cascade and axial charge decay\nis not as straightforward as predicted by the simplest form of anomalous\nMaxwell equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2015 15:25:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Sep 2015 15:01:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 May 2016 14:50:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2016 09:19:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-13"}
